<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Book</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="new.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="header.css">
</head>
<body>
 
    <form action="/new/books" method="POST">
 
        <h1>Add a New Book</h1>
        
        <label for="title">Title:</label>
        <input type="text" id="title" name="title" required>

        <label for="author">Author:</label>
        <input type="text" id="author" name="author" required>

        <label for="description">Description:</label>
        <textarea id="description" name="description" required></textarea>
   
        <label for="olid">Open Library ID:</label>
        <textarea id="olid" name="olid" required></textarea>

        <p>Note: You can find the Open Library ID by searching for the book on <a href="https://openlibrary.org/">Open Library</a> and copying the OLID (ex, OL27330967M) from the URL.</p>


        <button type="submit">Add Book</button>

        <button type="button" onclick="window.location.href='/'">Back to Home</button>

    </form>
    
</body>
</html>